caption.title: Inhibition of Cl - channels decreases CHIKV protein expression after infection at different MOIs.
caption.p: Huh7 cells were infected with CHIKV at an MOI 10 ( A) and MOI 0.1 ( B), respectively, and the intracellular expression levels of CHIKV nsP1 and capsid determined by western blot at 24 hpi.
